$lang['Similarly, after reaching 9 in Hexadecimal (represented by “F”), we start counting again at 10 (“10”). This pattern continues until we reach 15 (“1F”), at which point we reset back to 0 and begin counting again at 16 (“20”). This might sound confusing at first, but with a little practice, it will become second nature!'] = 'Mu ngeri y’emu, oluvannyuma lw’okutuuka ku 9 mu Hexadecimal (ekiikirira “F”), tutandika okuddamu okubala ku 10 (“10”). Enkola eno egenda mu maaso okutuusa lwe tutuuka ku 15 (“1F”), mu kiseera ekyo tuddamu okudda ku 0 ne tutandika okuddamu okubala ku 16 (“20”). Kino kiyinza okuwulikika ng’ekitabudde mu kusooka, naye bw’omala okwegezaamu katono, kijja kufuuka obutonde obw’okubiri!';
